    "body": "### Problem\n\nThe hover and signatureHelp widows are all very indented and do not scale with the content inside\n\nHover:\n![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3f01f1e6-2533-4c23-a944-a8ad3dfe7551)\n\nsignatureHelp:\n![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/d7c6a517-20ef-4a78-96a8-9b5fb4d89eed)\n\n\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nI set borders like this:\n\n```lua\nlocal orig_util_open_floating_preview = vim.lsp.util.open_floating_preview \nlocal orig_util_open_floating_preview = vim.lsp.util.open_floating_preview\nfunction vim.lsp.util.open_floating_preview(contents, syntax, opts, ...)\n  opts = opts or {}\n  opts.border = opts.border or \"rounded\"\n  return orig_util_open_floating_preview(contents, syntax, opts, ...)\nend```\n\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\n0.10.2\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nno\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nGentoo\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nfoot\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nfoot\n\n### Installation\n\nemerge nvim",
